Nutrient data for: CADBURY WISPA CHOCOLATE DRINK, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210141132
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: Sugar, skimmed MILK powder, maltodextrin, fat reduced cocoa powder (7.8%), glucose syrup, coconut fat, emulsifiers (SOYA lecithin, E471, E442, sunflower lecithin), flavorings, MILK, thickener (E407), salt, modified starch, anti-caking agent (E551), MILK proteins, cocoa mass, cocoa butter, vegetable oils (palm and shea in various proportions). Cocoa, Sugar: traded in compliance with Fairtrade Standards, total 51%. Visit www.info.fairtrade.net. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 07/26/2016
